{
  "texts": [
    "Training BLOOM requires 433 MWh of energy, and training GPT-3 requires1287 MWh 12.",
    "Approximating that a GPU lasts 1.5 years before becoming obsolete 20, the amortized training cost per query for BLOOM is 0.00004 g CO2e, and for GPT3 is 0.0001 g CO2e.",
    "Similarly, the embodied energy of the server used to conduct the query is approximately 2500 kg CO2e 12.",
    "Since, based on our own measurement, a GPT3 query takes approximately 3.8 s per page of text (4.4 s for ChatGPT to produce 292 words), the embodied energy of the server per query is 0.03 g CO2e.",
    "These values are several orders of magnitude lower than the energy footprint of training and conducting the query."
  ]
}